{"tid":2059770,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港台署理副廣播署長陳敏娟請辭","createTime":"2020-06-11T07:05:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-11T10:40:42.000Z","uid":124630,"like":126,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"1a7585af068a92b499bb01c37fcb495c77c24130","tid":2059770,"uid":124630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T07:05:01.000Z","msg":"署理副廣播處長陳敏娟因健康理由提出請辭，9月1日離任。港台節目製作人員工會表示，港台正值多事之秋，深表無奈，感謝陳敏娟捍衛編輯自主的努力，並尊重她的決定。<br />\n<br />\n工會表示，近月牽涉港台的爭議，包括商務及經濟發展局成立專責小組「檢討港台」、顧委會干預港台編輯方針、通訊局裁決、教育電視中心同事被逼遷等，陳敏娟主管節目製作，箇中壓力不足為外人道，在風雨飄搖之際離開港台，令人傷感。<br />\n<br />\n全文<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/715486135226112/posts/3535622429879121/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F715486135226112%2Fposts%2F3535622429879121%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=zXAIbGZ2Qohx5%2Bb7%2FAbjRJB82cw%2Bhl0zMn8EQHxvzrU%3D&h=d27e717d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/715486135226112/posts/3535622429879121/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"168b32327e9be57cc078bd0c43d14d55500ac0e3","tid":2059770,"uid":124630,"like":43,"dislike":0,"score":43,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T07:09:53.000Z","msg":"唉，唔知講咩好<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1fea7a60fdaf48435255c0b31d2847a47ea0224","tid":2059770,"uid":124630,"like":62,"dislike":3,"score":59,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T07:10:52.000Z","msg":"匯豐 國泰 今次到港台高層<br />\n唔順中共意都要走<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b65e4fddaab44ebb3bc7c93bb5a4111c07d60427","tid":2059770,"uid":124630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T07:12:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54b49fb5708a1eb5aa187af3e1f3bae18ad6d994","tid":2059770,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T07:12:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e2b934af3e3376043bf6a9b07f52a9db01da369","tid":2059770,"uid":1