":2059770,"uid":265192,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T07:18:03.000Z","msg":"港台官員未必係黃, 但起碼堅持公務員既操守同原則 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n走一個正常人, 又會多一個黨幹部入去 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f49e84dbbacb636816d214233e74c2cbf97746a6","tid":2059770,"uid":265192,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T07:18:53.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">因「未能促進synergy」 <br />\n港台署任助理廣播處長陳敏娟被拒坐正</span></strong><br />\n2016年07月14日<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.memehk.com/posts/16288\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.memehk.com%2Fposts%2F16288&d=zXAIbGZ2Qohx5%2Bb7%2FAbjRJB82cw%2Bhl0zMn8EQHxvzrU%3D&h=8405d224\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.memehk.com/posts/16288</a><br />\n<br />\n//最近有消息指，署任助理廣播處長職位逾一年、分別負責電台及電視運作的陳耀華及陳敏娟，原本預期今年皆獲「坐正」。但近日港台發表的內部通告卻只升陳耀華廣。據悉，播處長梁家榮曾在電視部高級製作人員內部會議，指出陳敏娟落選原因為「未能促進synergy（協作）」。有資深港台員工指以往未聽聞有相關評核指標，質疑陳敏娟被拒升職是因她屬堅守編輯自主及節目原則的少數派。//"},{"pid":"49dca024ed71e47b70f850806e467ce4a9b8ed77","tid":2059770,"uid":124630,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cd11dde26b24bc7a793e47ffd7f1dc97af983178","tid":2059770,"uid":265192,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T07:18:03.000Z","msg":"港台官員未必係黃, 但起碼堅持公務員既操守同原則 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n走一個正常人, 又會多一個黨幹部入去 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T07:20:10.000Z","msg":"佢係負責節目部分，點都有影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dece5bcf44db97a39b01ed1245325f4abf40e88e","tid":2059770,"uid":124630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T07:21:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14e7e4e2d7d6277509416437f460b892b231740a","tid":2059770,"uid":308251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit